snippet.title: Yedesna Shoots 3 - Play Testing Classic mode
snippet.description:
Yedesna Shoots 3 is planned to be the final and defenitive version of the series, it might take a while to release, classic mode is pretty much done though! It works pretty much the same as in the first version of the game.
I don't think I'll unlist the previous versions of the game, but to me they feel more like Alpha - Beta - Official Release..

You can find the attributes in the settings menu, made sure to include them clearly this time :)

If we used your work and you would like it removed, please contact us at: hayxuanimate@gmail.com, or well just leave us a comment :)
